data.description: Welcome home to this lovely Haley II floorplan by Mattamy Homes!  This home lives large at 2480 sf; 4BR, 3B (only Haley II w/3 Baths), Study and loft. It is loaded with beautifully appointed upgrades! Including hand crafted millwork added to several rooms throughout.  Enjoy entertaining guests in a designer kitchen w/upgraded cabinets, natural gas range/oven, quartz countertops and wine cooler. Relax on the covered lanai overlooking water views and cooking outdoors on the outdoor cooktop. There is plenty of storage in the three car tandem garage. Outdoor LED holiday lights. *Note- Bonus/ Option built in for Murphy bed, unfinished and ready for you to design to your taste.  A Must See & perfect for a family looking for great schools
